---
import profile from "../assets/profile.jpg";
import UserIcon from "../assets/icons/userIcon.astro";
import Phone from "../assets/icons/Phone.astro";
import GitIcon from "../assets/icons/GitIcon.astro";
import LinkedinIcon from "../assets/icons/LinkeinIcon.astro";
import TwitterIcon from "../assets/icons/TwitterIcon.astro";
---

<section class="aboutme w-3/4 h-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
  
  <h2 class="section-header text-6xl relative left-[200px] top-[25px]">
    ABOUT ME
  </h2>

  <div class="content flex flex-row w-full h-[400px] max-h-[400px]">

    <div class="sidebar flex flex-col justify-center items-center px-5 gap-5">

      <a href="#">
        <GitIcon class="link-icon fill-white size-7"/>
      </a>
      <a href="#">
        <LinkedinIcon class="link-icon fill-white size-7"/>
      </a>
      <a href="#">
        <TwitterIcon class="link-icon fill-white size-7"/>
      </a>

    </div>

    <div class="picture relative bottom-[30px] max-w-[300px] max-h-[200px] shrink-0">
      <img src={profile.src} alt="Johan's picture" />
    </div>

    <div class="info flex flex-col w-full gap-6 justify-center px-10">

      <div class="header-info text-lg text-accent">
        <h3>22 YEARS / DR / JUNIOR</h3>
      </div>

      <p class="text-sm text-justify max-w-md text-balance">
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Cras eu velit
        lacinia, egestas ex ac, vulputate orci. Sed dictum nulla vel feugiat
        feugiat. Vivamus a orci et nisl pharetra sodales et ac ipsum. Nullam
        porta, ante at euismod placerat, tortor orci dapibus nisl, non fermentum
        ante nisl at nisi. Donec pulvinar, nunc id accumsan dictum, nisl libero
        tristique sem, et ornare felis ex quis diam.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-row space-x-7">
        <a href="#" class="main-link flex flex-row justify-center items-center hvr-bounce-to-right w-44 h-10 text-xl gap-2">
          
          <UserIcon class="size-5"/>
          <span class="pb-1">CV</span>

        </a>
        <a href="#" class="secondary-link flex flex-row justify-center items-center hvr-bounce-to-right2 w-44 h-10 text-xl gap-2">
          
          <Phone class="size-5"/>
          <span class="pb-1">CONTACT</span>
          
       </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>

  .content {
    background: #101112;
    box-shadow: 0px 4px 100px 0px #000;
  }

  .section-header {
    font-family: Cera CY Bold;
  }

  .sidebar > a .link-icon {

    transform: scale(1,1);
    transition:ease 0.2s;

  }
  
  .sidebar > a:hover .link-icon {

    fill: var(--accent);
    transform: scale(1.5,1.5);
    transition:ease 0.2s;
    
  }

  p {
    font-family: Cera CY Regular;
  }

  .picture img {
    box-shadow: 0px 4px 50px 0px #000;
  }
</style>
